{"tid":2240201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國務院：支持國企與民企相互兼並重組","createTime":"2020-10-12T13:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T14:31:05.000Z","uid":98317,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"fb74ae89d13463b6503d377950f9ca395f19b12b","tid":2240201,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"10月12日，在國務院新聞辦公室舉辦的新聞吹風會上，國有資產監督管理委員會副主任翁傑明在回答記者提問時表示，從沒有在國企與民企兼並重組之間設置界限，支持相互兼並重組。翁傑明表示，要把握實事求是原則，只要兼並重組能提升企業競爭力，避免企業之間的無序競爭，適度提升產業競爭度，提升企業的國際競爭力，就應支持。 (澎湃新聞)"},{"pid":"1160fa6478387ecd5aa0048558f167ac4ac6e891","tid":2240201,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\non9仔發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4492138114977806b5fa578782923ca3397382d5","tid":2240201,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:22:40.000Z","msg":"國進民退2.0<br />\n大躍進人民公社準備"},{"pid":"406da23356dad3fbe9d6eafaf73d50eeac621204","tid":2240201,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"公私合營<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d7afd7147aafa3add05b5b0e5051244f39c178","tid":2240201,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">國務院新聞辦公室牌子掛在中共中央宣傳部，即係代表習近平嘅喉舌</span>"},{"pid":"ab843aacb19249aa12df62648155b0973f62c64f","tid":2240201,"uid":259901,"like"